quran[31]{c,v,t}:
  74,1,Yewe uwitwikiriye (uvugwa aha ni Intumwa Muhamadi)
  74,2,Haguruka uburire (ibiremwa)
  74,3,Unahe ikuzo Nyagasani wawe
  74,4,Unasukure imyambaro yawe
  74,5,Unitarure ibigirwamana
  74,6,Ntukanatange (ikintu) ugamije indonke zitubutse
  74,7,Kandi ujye wihangana kubera Nyagasani wawe
  74,8,Ubwo impanda izavuzwa
  74,9,Uwo munsi uzaba ari umunsi ukomeye
  74,10,Uzaba utoroheye abahakanyi
  74,11,(Yewe Muhamadi) ndekera uwo naremye ari wenyine (uvugwa aha ni Al Walid bun al Mughirat)
  74,12,Nkamuha imitungo itubutse
  74,13,N’urubyaro rumukikije
  74,14,Nkanamworohereza ubuzima
  74,15,"Nyuma y’ibyo byose, akaba yifuza ko namwongera"
  74,16,Oya! Mu by’ukuri yajyaga ahinyura amagambo yacu cyane
  74,17,Nzamunaniza muhanisha ibihano bikomeye
  74,18,Mu by’ukuri yaratekereje maze afata umwanzuro (wo gutuka Allah n’Intumwa ye ndetse na Qur’an)
  74,19,"Bityo, navumwe kubera umwanzuro yafashe"
  74,20,Niyongere avumwe kubera umwanzuro yafashe
  74,21,Nuko (yubura amaso) areba (abari bamukikije)
  74,22,"Maze azinga umunya, akambya agahanga"
  74,23,"Nuko atera umugongo (ukuri), maze aribona"
  74,24,Aravuga ati “Ibi (Muhamadi yigisha) nta kindi biri cyo uretse ko ari uburozi (akomora ku barozi bo hambere bakomeye)!”
  74,25,“Ibi (Muhamadi yigisha) nta kindi biri cyo uretse ko ari amagambo y’umuntu!”
  74,26,Nzamutwikira mu muriro
  74,27,N’iki cyakumenyesha uwo muriro
  74,28,Nta cyo ureka ndetse nta n’icyo usigaza
  74,29,Utwika imibiri ukanayishiririza
  74,30,Urinzwe (n’abamalayika) cumi n’icyenda
  74,31,"Kandi nta bandi twagize abarinzi b’umuriro batari abamalayika. Ndetse twanashyizeho umubare wabo (cumi n’icyenda) kugira ngo tugerageze abahakanyi, no kugira ngo abahawe ibitabo bemere badashidikanya (ko Qur’an ari ukuri kuko ihuriye kuri uwo mubare wanditse mu bitabo byabo); ndetse no kugira ngo abemeramana barusheho kwemera, no kugira ngo abahawe igitabo n’abemeramana batagira ugushidikanya (ku byo bemeye), ndetse no kugira ngo abafite uburwayi (bw’uburyarya) mu mitima n’abahakanyi bavuge bati “Allah yari agamije iki mu gutanga uru rugero?” Uko ni ko Allah arekera mu buyobe uwo ashaka akanayobora uwo ashaka. Kandi nta wamenya ingabo za Nyagasani wawe utari We. Kandi uyu (muriro) nta kindi uri cyo usibye ko ari urwibutso ku bantu"